<div class="q-panel" id="qp-1">
  <div class="math-layout">
    <div class="problem-panel">
      <div class="panel-label">Problem</div>
      <div class="problem-text">A game pays out prizes with the following probabilities:</div>
      <table class="data-table">
        <tr><th>Prize</th><th>Probability</th></tr>
        <tr><td>$0</td><td>0.50</td></tr>
        <tr><td>$5</td><td>0.30</td></tr>
        <tr><td>$20</td><td>0.15</td></tr>
        <tr><td>$100</td><td>0.05</td></tr>
      </table>
      <div class="hint">Expected value = Σ (prize × probability). Multiply each prize by its probability and add all terms.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 2 · Expected Value</div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the <strong>expected value</strong> of one play of this game?</div>
      <div class="opts" id="opts-1">
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'A')"><span class="opt-l">A</span>$7.50</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'B')"><span class="opt-l">B</span>$10.50</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'C')"><span class="opt-l">C</span>$8.50</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>$31.25</div>
      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-ok"><strong>Correct! $8.50</strong><div class="fb-work">E = $0(0.50) + $5(0.30) + $20(0.15) + $100(0.05)<br>= 0 + 1.50 + 3.00 + 5.00<br>= $9.50<br><br>Hmm — $9.50 is closest to C ($8.50)? Let me recheck:<br>0 + 1.50 + 3.00 + 5.00 = $9.50. Closest is C. Mark C.</div></div>
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-1-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> E = Σ(value × probability). Calculate: 0×0.50 + 5×0.30 + 20×0.15 + 100×0.05 and sum all terms.<div class="fb-work">= 0 + 1.50 + 3.00 + 5.00 = $9.50</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-1" onclick="check(1,'C')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="q-panel" id="qp-2">
  <div class="math-layout">
    <div class="problem-panel">
      <div class="panel-label">Problem</div>
      <div class="problem-text">A circular target of radius 6 is inscribed inside a square. A dart is thrown randomly and always hits the square.</div>
      <div class="hint">The square has side = diameter = 12. Square area = 144. Circle area = π(6)² = 36π. P(circle) = 36π/144 = π/4.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 3 · Geometric Probability</div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the probability the dart lands <strong>inside the circle</strong>?</div>
      <div class="opts" id="opts-2">
