        <div class="feedback" id="fb-2-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> P = circle area / square area. Circle area = π(6)² = 36π. Square side = diameter = 12, so area = 144. P = 36π/144.<div class="fb-work">= π/4 ≈ 0.785</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-2" onclick="check(2,'A')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

