      <span class="math-eq">i⁵⁴</span>
      <div class="hint">Divide 54 by 4: 54 ÷ 4 = 13 remainder 2. Remainder 2 → i² = −1.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 1 · Powers of i</div>
