        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(0,this,'C')"><span class="opt-l">C</span>−1</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(0,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>−i</div>
      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-ok"><strong>Correct! −1</strong><div class="fb-work">54 ÷ 4 = 13 remainder 2<br>Remainder 2 → i² = −1<br>i⁵⁴ = −1 ✓</div></div>
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-fail"><strong>Not quite.</strong> Divide 54 by 4 to find the remainder: 54 = 4(13) + 2, so remainder is 2. Remainder 2 corresponds to i² = −1.<div class="fb-work">54 mod 4 = 2 → i² = −1</div></div>
        <button class="btn-check" id="btn-0" onclick="check(0,'C')" disabled>Check answer</button>
      </div>
    </div>
