      <div class="hint">Rate A = 1/4 tank/hr. Rate B = 1/6 tank/hr. Combined rate = 1/4 + 1/6. Find common denominator: 3/12 + 2/12 = 5/12 tank/hr. Time = 1 ÷ (5/12) = 12/5 hours.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
