        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(0,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>6 meters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-ok"><strong>Correct! 7 meters</strong><div class="fb-work">w(w+5) = 84<br>w²+5w−84 = 0<br>(w+12)(w−7) = 0<br>w = 7 or w = −12 (reject negative)<br>Width = 7 m · Length = 12 m<br>Check: 7 × 12 = 84 ✓</div></div>
