      <div class="hint">By the remainder theorem, if (x−2) is a factor then p(2) = 0. Compute p(2): 8 + 8 − 10 + k = 0. Solve for k.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
      <div class="q-label">Question 3 · Remainder Theorem</div>
      <div class="q-text">What is the value of <strong>k</strong>?</div>
      <div class="opts" id="opts-2">
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(2,this,'A')"><span class="opt-l">A</span>k = −6</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(2,this,'B')"><span class="opt-l">B</span>k = 6</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(2,this,'C')"><span class="opt-l">C</span>k = −10</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(2,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>k = 2</div>
      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
