      </div>
      <div class="q-actions">
        <div class="feedback" id="fb-0-ok"><strong>Correct! 17 cm</strong><div class="fb-work">d = √(9²+12²+8²)<br>= √(81+144+64)<br>= √289 = 17 cm ✓<br><br>Note: 9-12-15 is a 3-4-5 triple (×3). But then √(15²+8²) = √(225+64) = √289 = 17. This is a 8-15-17 right triangle!</div></div>
