    <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Choose the form that answers the question</div><div class="tip-body">Max/min questions → convert to vertex form. Root/x-intercept questions → factor or use quadratic formula. y-intercept questions → read c from standard form. Don't convert unless you need to.</div></div>
