      <span class="math-eq">A = 8000(1 + 0.06/4)^(4t)</span>
      <div class="hint">Quarterly compounding: n = 4, r = 0.06. Substitute t = 5 years. Use calculator: 8000 × (1.015)^20.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-panel-inner">
